<C>__{billy}
<D>__{technically, it's all rock. the calcium in the bones is replaced during fossilization. but you can feel the difference. see? rough, smooth. rough, smooth.}
<A>__{he runs her bare fingers over the two different patches, showing her. after a pause, she runs her finger along his stubbly chin...}
